<?php $__env->startSection('content'); ?><p>After putting in incredibly hard work, she lost two stone following the birth of her second daughter, Sadie, nine months ago. </p>

<p>And Casey Batchelor was ensuring her gruelling labour was not for nothing as she continued in her fitness mission during her holiday in Lake Como. </p>

<p>On Thursday, the glamour model turned yoga enthusiast, 35, took to Instagram to show off her sensational figure in all its glory. </p>

<p>Stunner: Casey Batchelor was ensuring her gruelling labour was not for nothing as she continued in her fitness mission during her holiday in Lake Como</p>

<p>Casey looked incredible in her tiny black two-piece which showed off her peachy posterior and toned figure to perfection. </p>

<p>She paired the clip with a caption reading: 'Had a lovely swim this morning followed by my <?php echo e('@'); ?>yogablitz squat challenge with this dreamy view at <?php echo e('@'); ?>ghtlakecomo Even when I’m away I like to try and do some exercise in the morning...</p>

<p>'It makes me feel good and sets me up for the day. Which is why my <?php echo e('@'); ?>yogablitz is perfect as I can take it anywhere in the world with me on my phone or laptop head to www.yogablitz.com for the full squat challenge or link is in my bio'. </p>

<p>The Celebrity Big Brother star was recently inspired to up her fitness game with a 90-day fitness plan, and she unveiled her impressive weight loss in jaw-dropping before-and-after photos. </p>

<p>Wow: On Thursday, the glamour model turned yoga enthusiast, 35, took to Instagram to show off her sensational figure in all its glory</p>

<p> Transformation: Following the birth of her daughter, Sadie, nine months, the TV personality, 35, began a 90-day fitness plan and displayed the fruits of her labour in the social media post</p>

<p>She posted a snap of the impressive transformation alongside the caption: 'A little bit proud of myself guys! Not bad for reaching this goal after being stretched twice, having two babies in two years. </p>

<p>'Here's my 90 Day Challenge results and I've managed to lose 2 stone in 3 months. Last time it was 4 stone in 6 months so am thrilled to be losing at the same rate as last time, even though I've had cheat meals and even a whole week off!</p>

<p>'Am moving on to Bikini Blitz next so will let you know how I get on.' </p>

<p>Hot stuff: Casey looked incredible in her tiny black two-piece which showed off her peachy posterior and toned figure to perfection</p>

<p>The reality star announced the happy news that she had given birth to her second child, daughter Sadie, with fiancé Dane Goodson on January 26.</p>

<p>She originally announced she was pregnant with her second child in July, 14 months after welcoming first daughter Florence into the world.</p>

<p>The yoga instructor said although she and salesman fiancé Dane wanted to expand their family, they weren't prepared for how quickly it would happen.  </p>

